-- Juncker Says Greece May Need Additional Support, Maerkische Says
-- B y   J o s i a n e   K r e m e r
-- 2012-02-28T08:25:33Z
-- http://www.bloomberg.com/news/2012-02-28/juncker-says-greece-may-need-additional-support-maerkische-says.html
Greece  may require additional
support beyond the second bailout package, Luxembourg Prime
Minister  Jean-Claude Juncker , who also heads the group of euro-
area finance ministers, told Maerkische Allgemeine in an
 interview .  Juncker told the German newspaper that he can’t rule out
that further efforts will be needed given the uncertain
international situation, according to a transcript of the
interview published on the Luxembourg government’s website.
Juncker also said he doesn’t think Greece is heading toward a
disorderly bankruptcy.  To contact the reporter on this story:
